            "id": 6317822,
            "title": "【量大強漲股整理】台股震盪回檔下，【這族群】相對抗跌，會是下一波主角嗎?",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>台股震盪回檔下，【這族群】相對抗跌，會是下一波主角嗎?</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" src=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/6317822/l/2d48e2572b53e048321d9fdfa5decd0c.jpg\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">【量大強漲股整理】台股震盪回檔下，【這族群】相對抗跌，會是下一波主角嗎?(圖:shutterstock)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><div class=\"youtube-embed-wrapper\" style=\"position:relative;padding-bottom:56.25%;padding-top:30px;height:0;overflow:hidden;\"><iframe allowfullscreen=\"\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"360\" src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/9Ka5QE4Bing\" style=\"position: absolute;top: 0;left: 0;width: 100%;height: 100%;\" width=\"640\"></iframe></div></section><section>\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>影片中分享給你知道</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>(按讚訂閱打開小鈴鐺）</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><strong>再來看一下今天的台股</strong><strong>!</strong></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><strong><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>今日開低走低，終場下跌</strong><strong> 513.62</strong><strong> 點，收在</strong><strong> 31246.37</strong><strong> 點，成交量</strong><strong> 8689.00</strong><strong> 億。</strong></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><strong>觀察三大法人今天籌碼動向，外資賣超</strong><strong> 440.62</strong><strong> 億元，投信賣超</strong><strong> 175.96</strong><strong> 億元，自營商賣超</strong><strong> 157.52</strong><strong> 億元，三大法人合計賣超</strong><strong> 774.11</strong><strong> 億元，其中，外資、自營商連賣三日，投信則連賣十九日。</strong></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><strong>全球市場週三陷入劇烈震盪，美國總統川普再度拋出震撼彈，威脅要對歐洲國家加徵新關稅，以換取其控制格陵蘭島的政治野心，此舉引發全球政經局勢高度不確定性，恐慌指數</strong><strong> VIX </strong><strong>隨之飆升，美股主指週二集體下挫，<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊工業指數</a>重挫</strong><strong> 870 </strong><strong>點，<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">那斯達克</a>與<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數分別下跌</strong><strong> 2.3% </strong><strong>與</strong><strong> 1.6%</strong><strong>，指標股方面，</strong><strong>(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:NVDA:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/NVDA\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">NVDA-US</a>)</strong><strong> 輝達，</strong> <strong>與</strong><strong> (<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:TSM:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/TSM\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">TSM-US</a>)</strong><strong> 台積電</strong><strong> ADR</strong><strong>，</strong> <strong>雙雙重挫</strong><strong> 4%</strong><strong>，僅</strong><strong> (<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:MU:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/MU\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">MU-US</a>)</strong><strong> 美光，</strong> <strong>逆勢微漲</strong><strong> 0.6%</strong><strong>，川普政府已正式宣布將對</strong><strong> 8 </strong><strong>個北約成員國加徵</strong><strong> 10% </strong><strong>進口關稅，並威脅對法國葡萄酒、香檳徵收高達</strong><strong> 200% </strong><strong>的報復性關稅，歐盟方面已展開反擊討論，規模約</strong><strong> 1,080 </strong><strong>億美元的報復性方案正在醞釀中，瑞士達沃斯世界經濟論壇</strong><strong> 19 </strong><strong>日起舉行為期五天會議，市場正屏息關注川普美國時間</strong> (21 日) 發表演講，<strong>演說內容。</strong></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><strong>受美股重挫，加上今日<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/futures/TWF/TXF\">台指期</a>適逢結算，台股今日開低走弱，盤中一度重挫逾</strong><strong> 300 </strong><strong>點，跌破五日均線支撐約</strong><strong> 31,372</strong><strong> 點，終場下跌</strong><strong> 513.62</strong><strong> 點，收在</strong><strong> 31246.37</strong><strong> 點，成交量</strong><strong> 8689.00</strong><strong> 億，權值股走勢出現分歧</strong><strong> (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2330:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2330\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2330-TW</a>)</strong><strong> 台積電，</strong> <strong>收盤下跌</strong><strong> 1.97%</strong><strong> 至</strong><strong> 1,740 </strong><strong>元，法說會後股價進入高檔整理期；</strong><strong>(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2317:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2317\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2317-TW</a>)</strong><strong> 鴻海，</strong> <strong>開低震盪，回測</strong><strong> 219 </strong><strong>元，然而，電源龍頭</strong> <strong>；</strong><strong>(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2308:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2308\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2308-TW</a>)</strong><strong> 台達電，</strong> <strong>逆勢突圍，股價上漲</strong><strong> 0.44%</strong><strong> 至</strong><strong> 1,135 </strong><strong>元，續創歷史新高，此外，避險資金湧入金、銀市場，金價與銀價齊觸歷史新高，日本公債遭拋售導致殖利率飆升，加劇全球金融不安，美元匯價則小幅走軟。</strong></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><strong>展望後市，台股近期頻創新高，短線正乖離率確實偏大，今日的回檔可視為健康的「高檔換手」，川普的關稅政策雖造成地緣政治與金融市場的不安，但</strong><strong> AI </strong><strong>基礎建設的剛性需求並未消失，本週接下來的焦點將鎖定美國</strong><strong> PCE </strong><strong>通膨數據、</strong><strong>(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:NFLX:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/NFLX\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">NFLX-US</a>)Netflix</strong><strong>，</strong> <strong>與</strong><strong> (<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:INTC:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/INTC\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">INTC-US</a>)</strong><strong> 英特爾，</strong> <strong>的財報內容，以及日本央行的利率決策，投資人應避開漲幅已高的過熱權值股，轉向中小型成長股，<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>目前上升趨勢未變，多頭格局依然穩健。</strong></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><strong>重電族群今日表現相對強勢，</strong><strong>(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1514:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1514\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1514-TW</a>)</strong><strong> 亞力，觸及亮燈漲停至</strong><strong> 139.5 </strong><strong>元，</strong><strong>(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1519:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1519\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1519-TW</a>)</strong><strong> 華城，與</strong><strong> (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1513:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1513\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1513-TW</a>)</strong><strong> 中興電，皆有不錯漲幅，雖隨後漲幅收斂，但仍展現出內需基建與能源轉型的撐盤力道。</strong></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><strong>在</strong><strong> AI </strong><strong>產業面，</strong><strong>CPO</strong><strong> 族群，強勢表態</strong><strong>!</strong><strong> 更是佳螢領先點名的五大明星股之一，</strong></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><strong>光通訊股，受惠全球最大磷化銦基板供應商</strong><strong> (<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:AXTI:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/AXTI\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">AXTI-US</a>)AXT</strong><strong>，</strong> <strong>釋出樂觀預測，</strong><strong>2026 </strong><strong>年「機櫃間」訂單有望翻倍，市場預期共同封裝光學</strong><strong> CPO </strong><strong>業務將在</strong><strong> 2028 </strong><strong>年迎來爆發，長期趨勢未因短期關稅紛擾而改變。</strong></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><strong>2025.11.24</strong><strong> 股市期皇后節目領先預告</strong><strong> (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3081:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3081\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3081-TW</a>)</strong><strong> 聯亞</strong></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><figure><img src=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/6317822/l/6340820312d2aef53e4841411faf9851.jpg\"/></figure></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><strong>(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3081:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3081\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3081-TW</a>)</strong><strong> 聯亞</strong><strong>，</strong><strong>390 =&gt; 778</strong><strong> 領先預告後</strong><strong> +100%</strong><strong>，</strong><strong>在 AI</strong><strong> 伺服器升級與資料中心頻寬需求暴增帶動下，高速光通訊迎來關鍵轉折，矽光子及 800G</strong><strong>、1.6T</strong><strong> 光模組世代交替成為市場主軸，相關供應鏈評價快速重估，外資指出，800G</strong><strong> 與 1.6T</strong><strong> 產品將於 2026</strong><strong> 至 2028</strong><strong> 年加速滲透，矽光子可望成為資料中心主流架構，聯亞深耕 